{
  "stem": "26609.16",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I think they were all very wealthy, very elegant people, very well-dressed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She had big rooms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And when she took out her all-gold, you know, dinnerware, and [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] she took in from the, the wives of those people that worked in the fields for her.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they cleaned for weeks the cutlery and everything else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she-- and another one was a cook and used to cook for-- and bake days and nights even for those people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then one day came in a hoard of people, a lot of people, and with horses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they sat in a huge dining room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I've never opened the door to that dining room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they had big dinners.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I had to come in, because they didn't-- she didn't have enough people serving them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I ?] said, Wanda, if I can help out a little.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So there was another one who-- [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] like a waitress-- and told me only to help out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "As I came in there, into the-- very elegant people and everything was shining, you know, like you can see it like in picture sometimes, she-- not them, but she introduced me.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And she said, so here [GERMAN], my proud Pole, Polish girl, my proud-- [GERMAN], my proud Polish girl, how she introduced me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "When I was back, I went out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was through a hole opposite to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "One man came in from them, I remember a big, quite a big man, very elegant, grayish, [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] and got out a whole pack of money and said, Wanda, have it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I don't know if she told them or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "All these people were against Hitler, all of them, all against.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "She told me later.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
